Package extended_mitre.cwe

This package contains classes for work with CWE data - extended database structure
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CWEalterTermObj
    This class represents a CWE alternate term object (term attribute, description attribute)
    CWEapplPlatfObj
    This class represents a CWE applicable platform object (type attribute, class attribute, name attribute, prevalence attribute)
    CWEcategoryObj
    This class represents a CWE category object (CWE category id, category name attribute, category status attribute, category summary attribute, relationship objects (CWE ID, view ID), external reference reference objects)
    CWEconseqObj
    This class represents a CWE consequence object (scope attributes, impact attributes, note attributes, likelihood attributes)
    CWEdemExObj
    This class represents a CWE demonstrative example object (nature attribute, language attribute, content)
    CWEdetMethObj
    This class represents a CWE detection method object (method id attribute, method attribute, description attribute, effectiveness attribute, effectiveness notes attribute)
    CWEexampCodeObj
    This class represents a CWE demonstrative example - example code object (nature attribute, language attribute, content)
    CWEextRefObj
    This class represents a CWE external reference object (reference ID attribute, author attributes, )
    CWEextRefRefObj
    This class represents a CWE external reference reference object (section attribute, reference id attribute)
    CWEintrModesObj
    This class represents a CWE introduction (from modes of introduction) object (phase attribute, note attribute)
    CWEnoteObj
    This class represents a CWE note object (type attribute, content of the note)
    CWEobject
    This class represents a CWE object (CWE code (ID), name of weakness, abstraction attribute, structure attribute, ...)
    CWEobsExObj
    This class represents a CWE observed example object (reference attribute, description attribute, link attribute)
    CWEpotMitObj
    This class represents a CWE potential mitigation object (mitigation id attribute, phase attributes, strategy attribute, description attribute, effectiveness attribute, effectiveness notes attribute)
    CWErelationObj
    This class represents a CWE relation object (nature attribute, CWE code (ID) of related CWE, view_id attribute, ordinal attribute)
    CWErelationshipObj
    This class represents a CWE relationship (member) object (CWE ID attribute or CAPEC ID attribute, view ID attribute)
    CWEstakeholderObj
    This class represents a CWE stakeholder object (type attribute, description attribute)
    CWEtaxMapObj
    This class represents a CWE taxonomy mapping object (name, entry name attribute, entry ID, mapping fit attribute)
    CWEviewObj
    This class represents a CWE view object (CWE view ID, name attribute, type attribute, status attribute, objective attribute, filter attribute, relationship objects, note objects, external reference reference objects)
    CWEweakOrdObj
    This class represents a CWE weakness ordinality object (ordinality attribute, description attribute)
